        and the type of fireplace. We provide competitive, transparent pricing
        and detailed estimates.
      </p><h3><strong>Warranty on Fireplace Repair Services</strong></h3><p
        style="text-align: start">
        Our repair services come with a warranty, including 30 days of labor and
        up to 3 months for parts, affirming our dedication to quality and
        customer satisfaction.
      </p><h3><strong>Preventative Maintenance for Fireplaces</strong></h3><p
        style="text-align: start">
        We offer maintenance services to extend your fireplace's lifespan and
        ensure its optimal performance, including inspections, cleaning, and
        necessary adjustments or replacements.
      </p><h3><strong>Duration of Fireplace Repair Services</strong></h3><p
        style="text-align: start">
